Steps -

a) perl automate.pl <filename> , here filename is the one u want to analyze.

Before running automate.pl, you need to add the following format in slice.txt as well as in slice1.txt

filename lineno procedurename'variable   (Format). For example you can check the file silce and slice1.txt

b) Run this program and the output is stored in signature_final.txt. Before running automate.pl, make sure u delete all the  contents from signature_final.txt

c) Now, we run merge.pl. 

perl merge.pl filename signature_final.txt

The output is stored in slice_filename.c
